data.description: Lovely SINGLE STORY, home in very nice condition, 3 Bedroom 1 full bath and 2 3/4 Bath.  Perfect CULT-DE- SAC Street, very safe.  Family room w/Fireplace. Eating area in Kitchen, great open design that makes the family living space VERY COZY (OPEN SPACE), gives a unique feeling.  Brand-new free-standing STOVE with Oven, Dishwasher Microwave, nice modern overhead stove exhaust fan (lighted) living room with direct lighting, access to back yard thru a large glass sliding door, A/C and Central Heating. House faces East.  Direct entrance to Garage, Laundry hook-ups in garage  In ground pool, vinyl, gated with wrought iron.   Nice size yard, come and make an offer, you will be very happy here.
